     *
     * @param  value
     *         The long value to be written
     *
     * @return  This buffer
     *
     * @throws  BufferOverflowException
     *          If there are fewer than eight bytes
     *          remaining in this buffer
     *
     * @throws  ReadOnlyBufferException
